data.description: Nestled in a serene cul-de-sac, surrounded by lush trees, this one-story gem awaits you in the heart of a golf course community. Step inside & be greeted by the elegance of adjoining formals adorned w/ walls of windows, filling the space w/ natural light. The generously spacious eat-in kitchen boasts an abundance of cabinets & ample counter space. Take advantage of the convenient breakfast bar, an added bonus for quick & casual meals. Retreat to the rear of the home, & discover the oversized master bedroom, providing a tranquil haven for relaxation. The master bath features his/her sinks, complemented by white cabinets &  brightened by a skylight. Continuing down the hall, you'll find 3 well-proportioned secondary bedrms, offering plenty of space for family. Adjacent to these bedrooms, find a full bath. Venturing outside, a cvrd patio beckons, adorned w/ a charming wooden deck & surrounded by an oasis of shade-giving trees. Located within the highly regarded CFISD school district.
